SCORING.NAME: ions score
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The score provided for each Mascot peptide.

SCORING.NAME: standard score
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The score provided for each Mascot protein hit (it corresponds to the sum of ion scores).

SCORING.NAME: mudpit score
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The score provided for each Mascot protein hit when the number of MS/MS queries is high.

SCORING.NAME: modified mudpit score
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: A modified version of the MudPIT score computed by Proline.

SCORING.NAME: expect value
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The -log(E-value) provided by OMSSA for a peptide match.

SCORING.NAME: evalue log scaled
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The -log(expectation value) provided by Comet for a peptide match.

SCORING.NAME: evalue log scaled
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The -log(EValue) provided by MS-GF for a peptide match.

SCORING.NAME: expect log scaled
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The -log(expect) provided by Sequest for a peptide match.

SCORING.NAME: hyperscore
SCORING.DESCRIPTION: The hyperscore provided by X!Tandem for a peptide match.
